* Common Causes\nSpark Job Failures
** Code Errors
***_ Syntax errors
***_ Incorrect transformations
***_ Schema mismatches
***_ Data quality issues
***_ Error points directly to code
** Resource Bottlenecks
***_ Out-of-memory (OOM)
***_ Slow shuffle operations
***_ Repeated task failures
***_ Requires config tuning
** Environmental Issues
***_ Cluster startup failures
***_ Network problems
***_ External source unavailable
***_ Spot instance reclamation
***_ Account quota limits
@endmindmap
